# Security/Auth (If Implemented)

- **Roles:** ADMIN, LIBRARIAN, MEMBER.
- **ADMIN/LIBRARIAN only:** create, edit, delete; borrow/return.
- **MEMBER:** read/search; optionally view “My Loans”.
- Protect both UI and API; API protection is mandatory if auth exists.
